rows.label: tlk45100141_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I can't thank the mercenaries
here enough. Thanks to them, me
and my dad can live in peace!

rows.label: tlk45100141_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My dad's a scientist. He was being
chased by Invidian soldiers - they
wanted him to help develop weapons.

rows.label: tlk45100141_01_msg0004
rows.name:
They almost caught us, but
the mercenaries from here
showed up and saved us!

rows.label: tlk45100141_01_msg0005
rows.name:
They even gave us a place
to live and food to eat...they're
such great people!
